hrough 2032=E2=80=94putting the speculation to bed, at least for now.<br/><=
br/>Regardless, the investment in Round Mound Media <i>does not </i>imply i=
n any way that Barkley will produce a new NBA studio show to sell to the le=
ague=E2=80=99s new media partners.
